~ hud_menu
Tux: Need a quick brief, Nova?
- Where should I go right now?
	=> hud_pick_location
- What should I do next?
	=> hud_pick_objective
- Give me a world status check.
	=> hud_pick_world
- Read my vibe.
	=> hud_pick_tone
- How do I use the skill shop?
	=> hud_pick_shop
- Give me the full brief.
	=> hud_pick_full
- Never mind.
	=> hud_pick_exit

~ hud_pick_location
do choose_hud_topic_location()
=> END

~ hud_pick_objective
do choose_hud_topic_objective()
=> END

~ hud_pick_world
do choose_hud_topic_world()
=> END

~ hud_pick_tone
do choose_hud_topic_tone()
=> END

~ hud_pick_shop
do choose_hud_topic_shop()
=> END

~ hud_pick_full
do choose_hud_topic_full()
=> END

~ hud_pick_exit
do choose_hud_topic_exit()
=> END

~ hud_exit
Tux: Copy that. Ping me when you want another brief.
=> END

~ hud_location_tutorial_a
Tux: You are still in onboarding mode.
Tux: Lock in terminal basics now, and later zones will feel slower and clearer.
=> END

~ hud_location_tutorial_b
Tux: This area is your safe boot sandbox.
Tux: Test ideas here before you gamble in live Linuxia sectors.
=> END

~ hud_location_hamlet_a
Tux: Fallback Hamlet is your intel hub.
Tux: If direction gets fuzzy, talk to locals before forcing progress.
=> END

~ hud_location_hamlet_b
Tux: This town is stable for a reason.
Tux: NPC conversations here usually reveal your cleanest next move.
=> END

~ hud_location_forest_a
Tux: Filesystem Forest is full of misleading branches.
Tux: Trace clues carefully and do not trust the first route.
=> END

~ hud_location_forest_b
Tux: Forest sectors reward patience.
Tux: Read signs, inspect artifacts, and connect the dots before you sprint.
=> END

~ hud_location_depths_a
Tux: Daemon Depths is high-risk territory.
Tux: Keep your objective and fallback path in mind at all times.
=> END

~ hud_location_depths_b
Tux: Depths pressure people into bad decisions.
Tux: Stay deliberate and verify each interaction.
=> END

~ hud_location_vault_a
Tux: BIOS Vault is precision country.
Tux: One careful action beats three rushed ones.
=> END

~ hud_location_vault_b
Tux: Vault systems do not forgive sloppy reads.
Tux: Parse every prompt before you commit.
=> END

~ hud_location_unknown_a
Tux: This sector is not mapped in my quick index.
Tux: Scout first, commit second.
=> END

~ hud_location_unknown_b
Tux: Unknown zone detected.
Tux: Treat this area like a live incident: gather data before action.
=> END

~ hud_objective_no_tracker_a
Tux: I cannot read an objective tracker from here.
Tux: Use NPC dialogue as your temporary mission log.
=> END

~ hud_objective_no_tracker_b
Tux: Quest signal is unclear.
Tux: Re-anchor by talking to key NPCs and checking your journal flow.
=> END

~ hud_objective_no_active_a
Tux: No active quest is currently pinned.
Tux: Your next step is likely hidden behind a conversation trigger.
=> END

~ hud_objective_no_active_b
Tux: Tracker looks clean right now.
Tux: That usually means someone nearby has your next objective.
=> END

~ hud_objective_ready_a
Tux: You have a quest ready to check complete.
Tux: Confirm it now to unlock the next branch.
=> END

~ hud_objective_ready_b
Tux: One of your objectives is already finishable.
Tux: Cash it in before collecting new noise.
=> END

~ hud_objective_active_a
Tux: You have an active quest chain in progress.
Tux: Stay on that thread until the checkpoint closes.
=> END

~ hud_objective_active_b
Tux: Keep focus on your current objective.
Tux: Progress compounds when you finish one chain at a time.
=> END

~ hud_world_momentum_a
Tux: You have real momentum now.
Tux: Major blockers are falling; push high-value objectives while the path is warm.
=> END

~ hud_world_momentum_b
Tux: System state is opening up in your favor.
Tux: Convert this momentum into a major unlock.
=> END

~ hud_world_forest_key_a
Tux: Forest proficiency is online.
Tux: Find the missing fragmented link and the route should stabilize.
=> END

~ hud_world_forest_key_b
Tux: You unlocked forest systems but one chain is still incomplete.
Tux: Hunt the fragment and close that gap.
=> END

~ hud_world_gatepass_a
Tux: Gatekeeper pass is confirmed.
Tux: Your next leverage point is deeper access progression.
=> END

~ hud_world_gatepass_b
Tux: Passage is earned.
Tux: Now turn that permission into meaningful territory control.
=> END

~ hud_world_default_a
Tux: Linuxia is still shifting.
Tux: Keep collecting context from people, logs, and outcomes.
=> END

~ hud_world_default_b
Tux: World state is open-ended right now.
Tux: Dialogue clues are your fastest compass.
=> END

~ hud_tone_good_a
Tux: Your choices are building trust.
Tux: Keep leading with discipline and people will back you.
=> END

~ hud_tone_good_b
Tux: You are earning goodwill across the map.
Tux: That opens better doors than force ever will.
=> END

~ hud_tone_evil_a
Tux: Your actions are being noticed.
Tux: Expect resistance, tighter reactions, and fewer second chances.
=> END

~ hud_tone_evil_b
Tux: Fear can move systems quickly.
Tux: But it always leaves debt behind you.
=> END

~ hud_tone_neutral_a
Tux: Stay balanced.
Tux: Read, think, then act.
=> END

~ hud_tone_neutral_b
Tux: Your path is still flexible.
Tux: Next choices can tilt Linuxia in either direction.
=> END

~ hud_shop_hint_a
Tux: Open TERMINAL, then type: shop
Tux: That opens the skill graph where wget unlock commands are listed.
=> END

~ hud_shop_hint_b
Tux: The shop is terminal-driven here.
Tux: Use shop, then copy the wget unlock command for the skill you want.
=> END

~ hud_shop_ready_a
Tux: Your shop loop is online.
Tux: Keep using shop as your upgrade map before hard fights.
=> END

~ hud_shop_ready_b
Tux: You already unlocked core terminal upgrades.
Tux: Recheck shop between encounters to plan your next skill path.
=> END

~ hud_bios_tux_missing
Nova: Tux...? Where are you?
Nova: This place feels wrong without you.
=> END

~ hud_proprietary_tux_ahead
Nova: Oh, Tux is right up ahead.
=> END
